data.description: This 3 BR/2BA lovely home is convenient to Carrollton and Villa Rica. The front yard is large and beautifully green in the summer! The front porch and wrap around deck features a porch swing spot and plenty of room for grilling and cooking out. The huge fenced in backyard has mature trees and a shed and awaits animals or children to play and run freely! Newer HVAC (2019), new roof, porch, deck, newer hot water heater and all new windows. The fireplace is wood burning for those chilly and cold evenings in the fall and winter, should you so desire! Dual fuel gas/electric heating and cooling. The family room is roomy with high ceilings and connects to the kitchen. Plenty of counter and cabinet space with newer counters.  Call today to schedule your appointment! $239,000.
